Source: mdserve
Section: misc
Maintainer: Local Builder <builder@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl
Homepage: https://github.com/jfernandez/mdserve

Package: mdserve
Architecture: amd64
Description: Markdown preview server for AI coding agents.
 mdserve is a zero-config markdown preview server designed as a live
 rendering companion for AI coding agents. It supports instant live
 reload, GitHub Flavored Markdown tables, code blocks, and Mermaid
 diagrams.
